B) Correct

With Lambda proxy integration enabled, the Lambda function must return a JSON object with the following structure:

{
 "statusCode": 400,
 "headers": {
 "Content-Type": "application/json"
 },
 "body": "{\"message\": \"Invalid request\"}"
}

If the statusCode is omitted or incorrectly set, API Gateway defaults to returning a 200 status code.
